data.description: Great floorpan, large kitchen with many cabinets, 3BR, 2.5BA, 2-stall garage home and only 1.5 miles from Downtown Gilbert Heritage District. Conveniently located across the street from the community park, a few minutes walk to the community pool, and abuts to the Heritage Trail Canal.  Many updates were done in 2020 to include porcelain wood look plank tile flooring throughout downstairs and in the upstairs bathrooms/laundry, granite countertops, new AC, and new hot water heater.  New refrigerator and washing machine installed in 2023. Spacious open floor plan with living/dining, kitchen island with cabinets, ample counter space, numerous honey maple cabinets, pantry, and large under-stairs storage. Upstairs are three bedrooms and the laundry room. Ceiling-hung storage in garage conveys.
